posting_body: ['Bright Studio at The Oakview Apartments', 'Property Address', '616 Lincoln Ave - 105 | St. Paul, MN 55102', 'Available: 09/02/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Bright Studio at The Oakview Apartments', 'This charming studio has West facing views out over Dale Street for amazing afternoon sunlight.', 'Original built-in kitchen cabinets, hardwood floors throughout, and a walk-in closet!', 'Built in 1919, the Oakviews offer both studio and one bedroom apartment homes to choose from that will be sure to please.', 'The one bedroom apartments are unique Pullman rail-car inspired plans with dramatic French windows in the living rooms.', 'The studio apartments feature over-sized walk-in closets and eat-in kitchens.', 'All apartment homes feature hardwood floors, pedestal sinks, and original built-in cabinetry for the historical flair but updated appliances and fixtures combined with new windows give the buildings a modern feel.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Heat Paid', 'Water Paid', 'Trash Paid', 'Controlled Entry', 'On-Site Laundry', 'On-Site Rental Office', 'Clubhouse and Fitness Center One Mile Away', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 400', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $890.00', 'Available: 09/02/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
